---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Home from '../../components/Home.astro';

---

<Layout>
    <Home />
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <!-- 使用説明 -->
<section id="how-to" class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800">
<h3><i class="fa-solid fa-question"></i>CompareJSON 使用説明</h3>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-16">
<div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-lg">
<div class="flex items-center mb-2">
<div class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/50 text-green-600 dark:text-green-300 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
<i class="fas fa-keyboard"></i>
</div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-medium">データの入力方法にはいくつかありますか?</h4>
 </div>
 <!-- <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm space-y-2 pl-3">
 {t("explain.input.desc1")} </br>
 {t("explain.input.desc2")} </br>
 {t("explain.input.desc3")} </br>
 </p> -->
 <ul>
 <li>1. 文本框中直接貼付JSON内容</li>
 <li>2. 点击上传图标选择本地JSON文件</li>
 <li>3. JSON 文を上の传領域に放り出す</li>
 </ul>

 </div>
 <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-700rounded-lg">
 <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
 <div class="bg-rose-100 dark:bg-rose-900/50 text-rose-600 dark:text-rose-300 w-8 h-8rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
